title: Sellas Tetteh and Sierra Leone suffer shock defeat at Chad in 2018 FIFA World Cup qualifier
text:
Sports News | 10 October 2015 23:25 CET Sellas Tetteh and Sierra Leone suffer shock defeat at Chad in 2018 FIFA World Cup qualifier - www.ghanasoccernet.com Sellas Tetteh 
Ghanaian coach Sellas Tetteh and his Sierra Leone side suffered a 1-0 defeat at Chad in their 2018 FIFA World Cup preliminary round first leg tie. 
The Leone Stars conceded just after half-time at Stade Omnisports Idriss Mahamat Ouya in N'djamena on Saturday. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
